{"tid":2065480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"梁手足，我沒有什麼可以做，今天只有這些","createTime":"2020-06-15T14:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T02:54:40.000Z","uid":201027,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1299712724c3ac1f927e79db74fc3254e63ec5","tid":2065480,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"今天我只能黑衫黑褲，<br />\n在胸前扣上白絲帶，<br />\n把手上的白花放在太古廣場對出的地上，<br />\n早已變成一片花海的地上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實說，我的親人離世，<br />\n我也沒有天時暑熱、山長水遠為他們獻上鮮花。<br />\n他們在沒有不公義的牽連下安祥地走了。<br />\n我也懷念他們，一切在心中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那延綿至花園道纜車站的人龍，<br />\n是在世手足對生命、對香港的熱愛，<br />\n我們一定會代你和離世的手足走下去，<br />\n直至光復香港那天！<br />\n<br />\n2020.6.15<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjSott3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjSott3.png&h=dac44a1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"986af8f8e67f8cac434b0eac934ce2e1fbea5b9d","tid":2065480,"uid":201027,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:52:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立<br />\n唯一出路</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"07af0a1dd214c1c0c851364254330b8219a697c7","tid":2065480,"uid":201027,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"944fa5dab9df82e936582251ab83518654915aee","tid":2065480,"uid":281492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf85ec167e48dbe2e043adfa1554b4a333a83332","tid":2065480,"uid":240004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"以後每年6月15號都係香港既Remembrance day<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13db428ed9bd121da3e65a7f